# Templating Rules

## Handlebars Templates
- Use Handlebars (.hbs) for server-side templating
- Separate into layouts, partials, pages
- Use layout templates for consistent structure
- Create reusable partials for components
- Keep client-side JavaScript minimal

## CSS & Styling
- NEVER use inline styles
- ALWAYS use external CSS files
- Organize CSS by component in `app/public/styles/`
- Use CSS classes/IDs, not inline attributes
- Mobile-first responsive design

## Structure
```
app/templates/
├── layout.hbs           # Main layout
├── partials/            # Reusable components
└── exif/                # EXIF mappings

app/public/styles/
├── styles.css           # Main styles
├── data-tree.css        # Component styles
└── [component].css       # Other components
```

